## Introducing new CORE
We’re creating a better way for you to submit CORE data: faster, simpler and built from the ground up with the user at the centre. We’re now looking for forward-looking organisations to help perfect our new service.

New CORE is ready to accept your data for 2021/22, and you can get early access before everybody else.

Have you been put off the idea of submitting CORE logs in the past? Want to find out how the new service could help you? Here are a few reasons why you might want to start using new CORE today.
