## A service for everybody
However you use new CORE, it’s accessible to everybody: whether that’s on paper, mobile, tablet or using a screen reader or other technology.

You told us the questions are complicated and difficult to understand. By breaking the form up into logical sections with only one question on every page, we’ve made the content clear and easier to digest.
