## We’re supporting the ways you work
It’s not just the CORE website we’ve redesigned. Filling in a log on paper is easier now too. 

We’ve split the form up into handy sections, so you can print the parts you need when interviewing tenants. Or save even more time and part-fill your logs using data from your housing management system.

And if you or your organisation prefer to go paperless, fill CORE in anytime, anywhere on your mobile or tablet.
